	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator in 44. As one of the conspirators against Caesar (App. BC 2.113), he was probably a senator in 44. On the name, see ILS 5578-ILLRP 609. See Wiseman, CQ 14, 1964, 131; NM 262, no. 409. (TJC)\n" ;
